<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Healthy Food Guide</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <style>
    body {
      position: relative;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fff8;
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #28a745;
    }

    .navbar-brand,
    .nav-link {
      color: white !important;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 70px 20px;
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    #fruits {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
    }

    #vegetables {
      background-color: #fffde7;
    }

    #drinks {
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #28a745;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body data-spy="scroll" data-target="#foodNav" data-offset="60">

  <!-- Horizontal Scrollspy Navigation -->
  <nav id="foodNav" class="navbar navbar-expand-sm sticky-top">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Healthy Food</a>

    <ul class="navbar-nav">
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#fruits">Fruits</a>
      </li>

      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#vegetables">Vegetables</a>
      </li>

      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#drinks">Healthy Drinks</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">

    <div id="fruits" class="section">
      <h2> Fruits</h2>
      <p>Fruits are rich in vitamins, minerals, and fibre. Apples, bananas, and oranges help keep our bodies healthy.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="vegetables" class="section">
      <h2> Vegetables</h2>
      <p>Vegetables provide important nutrients that help us grow strong. Eat a variety of colourful vegetables every day.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="drinks" class="section">
      <h2> Healthy Drinks</h2>
      <p>Milk, fresh fruit juice, and water are healthy drinks that keep us energetic and hydrated.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
